						<summary>

						<p>Slab build into the steps behind the <hi rend="italic">Kalyāṇa-maṇḍapa</hi> at the Surabhēśvara temple.</p>						

						<p>Sadāśiva 1553 A.D.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1475, Virōdhikṛit, Kārttika śu, 11.</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1553 A.D. October 17, Tuesday (the cyclic year was Pramādi).</hi></p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to register a gift of certain villages in the Ēṟuva-<hi rend="italic">sīma</hi> to the god Surabhēśvara by Daḷavāyi Veṁgaḷanāyuḍu, the <hi rend="italic">Karyakartta</hi> of <hi rend="italic">Mahāmaṇḍalēśvara</hi> Eṟṟa-Tirumalayyadēva Mahārāya.</p>						

						</summary>
